## Database
- 380+ tables, 25 enum types, 420 migrations
- RLS policies on ALL public tables (276 tables, all RLS enabled)
- Two plan systems: Subscription plans (`plans` table, tier_level 0-4) + Program plans (`program_plans`, per-enrollment)
- Dual credit system: individual (`user_credit_balances`) + org (`org_credit_balances`)
- `useEntitlements` hook merges subscription + program plan + add-ons + tracks + org-sponsored access

## Shared Services (`src/lib/`)
- `guidedPathInstantiation.ts` â€” `instantiateTemplate()` creates goals/milestones/tasks from guided path templates with pace-adjusted dates. Used by both survey wizard and manual "Copy This Path" dialog. `estimateCompletionDate()` for preview before instantiation.
- `assessmentScoring.ts` â€” `calculateDomainScore()` (simple + weighted averages), `calculateTypeScores()` (cross-domain type averages for radar charts), `parseQuestionTypes()`, `validateTypeWeights()`. 16 unit tests.
- When tables are not yet in generated Supabase types, use `as string` cast on table names: `.from("table_name" as string)`

